data.description:
The peaceful, happy and healthy lifestyle you are hoping for starts here in this established, low maintenance brick on slab home! The 1 level floor plan offers a formal living entry, comfy feeling family room with open concept dining and kitchen, laundry room, 3 good size bedrooms, and 2 full baths. 
Outside you have a private feeling overlooking 600+ acres of ranch land offering a beautiful view for morning sunrises and coffee, or evening stargazing. Corner lot with established grass and trees offers your pick of spots to relax and enjoy the scenery. 
This corner lot ranch style home is set in a sought-after neighborhood. The proximity to Luling’s 9 hole golf course, San Marcos River and Zedler Mill Park, and downtown restaurant and shopping scene makes it even that much more desirable. You’ll want to make time to get to know this one if you are trying to find a lovely home in an easy commuter location that Luling offers outside the fast-paced city living.
